reviewText: I absolutely love watching this movie. The Only downside is that there no english subtitles on when I watch it. Thats okay though, the good thing is that you can pretty much tell what everyone is saying if you use your imagination. Besides you don't need subtitles to watch a fun fight. Always remember two things though when buying any region dvd. Make sure you have the right all region dvd player & check the language/subtitles out first. You should be good if you do.
I like this movie. it's fun and I an joy it I been a Power Rangers fan since I was a kid.
